==Parties and elections== {{Main|List of political parties in Tuscany|Elections in Tuscany}}
===Latest regional election=== {{Main|2015 Tuscan regional election}}
In the latest regional election, which took place on 31 May 2015, [[Enrico Rossi (politician)|Enrico Rossi]] of the [[Democratic Party (Italy)|Democratic Party]] was re-elected for a second term. [[Claudio Borghi (politician)|Claudio Borghi]] of [[Lega Nord]] came distant second. The Democrats were by far the largest party with 46.3% of the vote. {{:2015 Tuscan regional election}}
